testimonials.name: Lina M., Product Designer at Flowcraft
testimonials.text: As a UI/UX designer, I've tried countless design systems, but ui-light hits the sweet spot between flexibility and simplicity. It keeps my workflow clean and fast without getting in the way.

testimonials.name: Jason K., Frontend Developer
testimonials.text: ui-light is a breath of fresh air for developers. The class naming is intuitive, the setup is minimal, and it plays perfectly with modern React projects. I've never built responsive UIs this fast.

testimonials.name: Anita S., Indie App Creator
testimonials.text: I love how lightweight and performant ui-light is. No unnecessary bloat, just the core utilities I need to build sleek interfaces. It made my apps noticeably faster!

testimonials.name: Daniel T., UI Team Lead at Nexlo
testimonials.text: Switching to ui-light helped our team streamline our UI development. Designers and developers are now totally in sync, thanks to the clean and consistent utility-first approach.

testimonials.name: Mira L., Freelance Web Developer
testimonials.text: Beautifully minimal, surprisingly powerful. ui-light strips away the noise and gives you just enough to build polished UIs without overcomplication.
